Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭 好丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都溼成這樣 還這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直人欺負人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厲害啊 都看光光了 結衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭 好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:03:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直人也…讓結衣子的身體感到舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好想要…直人 求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我你的精子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託讓結衣子懷孕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直人的…直人的那個流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 直人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是因為我無法懷孕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這都是因為這個家的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久以前就有的習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結衣子小姐 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是正和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了嗎 正和哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你到後院去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉 感覺今晚又會難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的名字叫燐堂直人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是代代相傳 燐堂家的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在戰後混亂的情況下 由當地居民所組成的大型組織"燐堂組"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會這麼壯大的原因 是在於每三代就要舉行一次的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之後我被當成了緋月家的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了嗎 直人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次不許你手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然沒辦法讓正和的妻子結衣子懷孕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 結衣子的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,緋月家的鮎美、美津菜、詩乃 不管誰都好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要讓其中一個生下你的繼承人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結衣子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 結衣子姐沒辦法懷孕不是她的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 那就是因為你的種太虛了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是這樣的 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 雖然覺得你原來的未婚妻 因為車禍而喪身很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 直人 燐堂家所受的古老詛咒是非常深的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又來了 一直詛咒詛咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你有在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到四月為止  如果沒辦法讓緋月家的女人懷孕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就把你逐出燐堂家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逐…逐出！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣 我現在正往結衣子的妹妹 居住的公寓前進中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,養育緋月姐妹長大的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸一老爺去海外旅行一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在公寓裡就只有那三姐妹而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直人就趁這一個月 對那些女孩播種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法啊 詩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些全部都是燐堂家決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我一定要當那種男人的對象啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐 妳想讓我們的生活都被打亂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們之所以能過這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都是托直人的本家"燐堂組"的福 妳應該知道吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奢侈、豐盛的飯菜、豪華的住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我離開這個家就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啊 詩乃 拜託妳冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是姐姐妳拜託我 我死也不生小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鮎美呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我從來都沒考慮過生小孩這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 聽我說 我們緋月家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,懷孕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓女性體內的受精卵呈現發育的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還真難搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要她們心甘情願的懷孕 哪有這麼容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要把你逐出燐堂家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉 我知道了 做就是了、做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼要去誰的房間呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個女的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果遇到抵抗的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我一定要當那種男人的對象啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 這個也會抵抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼就剩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然就只有她了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鯰…鮎美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？你在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手 等一下 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住…住手 等…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託不要看 拜託你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好過份 竟然這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 我太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一次看到妳 覺得妳不會反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…我沒照約定生小孩的話 就會被逐出家門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 一下子就急了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全沒有考慮到妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那個 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來 請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然 最容易成功的是鮎美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一個目標就決定是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我轉學到鮎美讀的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後 在那邊也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 不知道你喜不喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 有討厭的食物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鮎美完全不在意外界的眼光 對我十分的親切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是那種比想像中親切 奉獻自己的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我內心真的十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃、好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的作的到嗎？ 幫直人生小孩這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算那是我的命運 但是這種事… 我實在是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是接吻 做過之後就覺得沒有什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧 什麼都不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭 不要看 好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以…那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鮎美 直接叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直…直人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝妳 鮎美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以摸那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行…直人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直人 饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也來摸摸我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是男孩子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在姐姐的房間裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四女美津菜 好像偷看我和鮎美的行為
